    "Research indicates that exposure to misinformation, including deepfakes, can affect memory and the perceived accuracy of information [103].",
    "Studying how deepfakes impact cognitive processes is essential for comprehending the potential distortion of individuals' beliefs and memories.",
    "Furthermore, deepfakes pose a challenge to trust in media and information sources.",
